{"tid":910994,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【溫子仁效應？】《水行俠》預售贏《復仇者3》《毒魔》","createTime":"2018-11-21T14:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T18:56:01.000Z","uid":52215,"like":9,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"79c36f950fb0fbe61255db5db4553427aa8167b2","tid":910994,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:27:12.000Z","msg":"【溫子仁效應？】《水行俠》預售贏《復仇者3》《毒魔》<br />\n4小時前5.3K<br />\n即時娛樂<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《水行俠》預售成績厲害。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勁過《毒魔》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《復仇者3》將於聖誕節25號當日於Netflix上架。<br />\n<br />\nDC大作《水行俠》（Aquaman）下個月尾先喺北美地區開畫，但第一日嘅預售成績已經非常厲害，成績仲勁過Marvel今年嘅大作《復仇者聯盟3:無限之戰》（Avengers:Infinity War）首日預售紀錄，再贏埋另外兩部今年嘅大作《毒魔》（Venom）及《職業特工隊：叛逆之謎》（Mission:Impossible-Fallout）。有指因為粉絲對導演溫子仁相當有信心，所以先至有咁高期待。<br />\n<br />\n另外，串流電視台Netflix亦公佈將於聖誕節25號當日，將《復仇者聯盟3:無限之戰》上架，等大家可以睇住英雄片過節。但因為Netflix同迪士尼嘅合約就快到期，而電視台亦無權再播映2019年嘅Marvel英雄片，因此《復仇者3》就好可能係Netflix最後一套嘅迪士尼Marvel電影。<br />\n<br />\n廣告"},{"pid":"fe50894f706f81c72eab051866e87049d63abf5a","tid":910994,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e857f9550e1f4a1a9160938ac3cd3a0d1c2d8e","tid":910994,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:41:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d738fbf75df33c2efeeb7eb7bf6648c1a96346b","tid":910994,"uid":186784,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:57:08.000Z","msg":"Dc又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330a429281ed1ed53ec6a5a12aec229c85be88d6","tid":910994,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T02:11:18.000Z","msg":"Dc或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"55d6a1bb50ece2490f0433fc338c12d94f12dbf0","tid":910994,"uid":81914,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:50:34.000Z","msg":"毒魔就算吧啦 普通英雄片 但贏報